## Third-party components

This repository references but does not vendor the following upstream projects.
Each is governed by its own license:

- **Gstack** — https://github.com/garrytan/gstack (cloned at session start by
  the bootstrap hook; see that repo for its license)
- **Superpowers** — https://github.com/obra/superpowers (concepts referenced
  in simon-tdd / simon-worktree; no code vendored)
- **everything-claude-code** — https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code
  (concepts referenced in simon-instincts / simon-research; no code vendored)

The simon-stack skills, install scripts, hooks, templates, and documentation
in this repository are original works released under the MIT license above.
